  <h2>Responsive DiVE table</h2>
  
 <p>Create responsive tables by wrapping any <code>.table</code> in <code>.table-responsDiVE</code> to make them transform in <strong>inline table</strong> (under 768px). When viewing on anything larger than 768px wide, you will not see any difference in these tables.<br><br>

To display the heading of a column in the inline responsive view remember to include the <code>data-title</code> like <code> data-title="heading on responsive:"</code> as shown in the examples below.
 </p>
 <p>
<span class="label label-success">Note!</span> Thanks to advanced media-queries implementation and <code>data-title</code>; no javascript is requested!
